quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,Jab aasman phatt jayega
  84,2,Aur apne Rubb kay famaan ki tameel karega aur uske liye haq yahi hai (ke apne Rubb ka hukum maney)
  84,3,Aur jab zameen phaila di jayegi
  84,4,Aur jo kuch uske andar hai usey bahar phenk kar khaali ho jayegi
  84,5,Aur apne Rubb ke hukum ki tameel karegi aur uske liye haq yahi hai (kay uski tameel karey)
  84,6,Aey insaan tu kashaan kashaan apne Rubb ki taraf chala ja raha hai(striving unto your Lord) aur ussey milney wala hai
  84,7,Phir jiska naam-e-aamal uske seedhey haath mei diya gaya
  84,8,Ussey halka hisaab liya jayega
  84,9,Aur woh apne logon ki taraf khush khush paltega
  84,10,Raha woh shaks jiska naam-e-aamal us ki peeth ke pichey diya jayega
  84,11,To woh maut ko pukarega
  84,12,Aur bhadakti hui aag mei ja padega
  84,13,Woh apne ghar walon mein magan tha
  84,14,Usne samjha tha ke usey kabhi palatna nahin hai
  84,15,"Palatna kaise na tha, uska Rubb uske kartoot dekh raha tha"
  84,16,Pas nahin mai kasam khata hon shafaq(twilight) ki
  84,17,Aur raat ki aur jo kuch woh sameith leti hai
  84,18,Aur chaand ki jabke woh maah-e-kaamil (full) ho jata hai
  84,19,Tumko zaroor darja ba darja ek haalat se dusri halat ki taraf guzarte chalay jana hai
  84,20,Phir in logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh imaan nahin laatey
  84,21,Aur jab Quran inke samney pada jata hai to sajda nahin karte
  84,22,Balke yeh munkireen to ulta jhutlatay hain
  84,23,Halaanke jo kuch yeh (apne naam-e-aamal mein) jama kar rahey hain Allah usey khoob janta hai
  84,24,Lihaza inko dardnaak azaab ki basharat dedo
  84,25,Albatta jo log imaan le aaye hain aur jinho ne neik aamal kiye hain unke liye kabhi khatam na honay wala ajar hai